## 📂 Dataset

This project uses the **CREMA-D (Crowd-Sourced Emotional Multimodal Actors Dataset)**.

🔗 Download Dataset:
https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/ejlok1/cremad

### 📖 Description
CREMA-D is a speech emotion dataset containing audio recordings from actors expressing different emotions such as happy, sad, angry, fearful, and neutral.

### ⚠️ Note
Due to the large size of the dataset, it is not included in this repository.

### 📥 How to Use
1. Download dataset from the link above  
2. Extract the files  
3. Place them inside the `dataset/` folder  
4. Run the project  
